          "$m$g": "Politics heated up over a flag raising ceremony held by the PLA in Galwan ; the issuing of �standardised� names for 15 places in Arunachal Pradesh by the Chinese Ministry of Civil Affairs; the construction of a bridge across Pangong Lake by China; and a letter from the Chinese Embassy in New Delhi to MPs protesting their attendance at a Tibet event.",
