          "$m$g": "If Russia invades Ukraine, it could sharply change how the US deals with Iran. Not only would American attention be diverted, but Washington could hastily seek an interim deal, which Israel strongly opposes and which could drive Jerusalem towards more cyber attacks opn Nantaz.",
