          "$m$g": "Just when you think it couldn't get any worse - South Korea called  for Japan's retraction of a push to list a former mine linked to wartime forced labor as a UNESCO World Heritage Site. Why is this derailing relations ? US tries to straddle the diplomatic fence.",
